val importYearRaw = sc.textFile("/spark/customs/year/iy*.txt")

val importYear = importYearRaw.filter(_.startsWith("20"))
                              .map(_.split("\t"))
                              .filter(s => s(2) != "")
                              .map(s => Import(s(0), s(2),
                                              s(3).replaceAll("\"", ""),
                                              s(4).replaceAll("\"", "").replaceAll(",", "").toLong,
                                              s(5).replaceAll("\"", "").replaceAll(",", "").toLong))

importYear.toDF().write.saveAsTable("importYear")

// 수출통계와 수입통계를 하나로 합치기 위한 테이블 정
%sql
create table year_v0 (
    expPeriod VARCHAR(10),
    expCountry VARCHAR(30),
    expName VARCHAR(50),
    expWeight BIGINT,
    expAmount BIGINT,
    impWeight BIGINT,
    impAmount BIGINT,
    impPeriod VARCHAR(10),
    impCountry VARCHAR(30),
    impName VARCHAR(50)
)
paragraphs.title: 2. 수출입 통계 통합

paragraphs.text:
%sql -- Join 연산을 통한 수출입통계의 통
insert into year_v0
select e.period, e.country, e.name, expWeight, expAmount, impWeight, impAmount, i.period, i.country, i.name
from exportyear e full join importyear i on (e.period = i.period AND e.country = i.country AND e.name = i.name)

%sql
select * from year_V0
where expcountry is null or impcountry is null
